    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. The car has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a VANOS system refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain structural rigidity under high torque loads. With a functional variable M differential lock and a responsive MacPherson/multi-link suspension setup, this chassis offers the telepathic handling and mechanical feedback enthusiasts crave. A mechanically sound example with a clean power band and firm compression.",
