    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i in a stunning Deep Sea Blue Metallic finish. This vehicle has been driven with care and primarily garaged, preserving the deep luster of its paint, though a few minor stone chips on the front fascia reflect its honest road history. Inside, you\u2019ll find a spacious, smoke-free cabin appointed in Canberra Beige Dakota leather. The interior remains in impressive shape, with only slight softening of the driver\u2019s side bolster from regular use. All technological features, including the panoramic sunroof, navigation system, and Harman Kardon surround sound, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound; it comes with a complete service log from authorized dealerships, including a recent brake fluid flush and oil change. The Continental tires still offer plenty of life with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a solid, dependable luxury SUV that balances performance with everyday utility, perfect for a buyer seeking premium quality and peace of mind.",
